    "name": "Disarming Smile",
    "prerequisite": "*Empathetic Envoy*",
    "requirement": "You are aware of the attacker, the attacker is an intelligent humanoid creature, and you have not attempted to harm the attacker.",
    "subtype": "feat",
    "success": "Your foe pauses momentarily. Their attack fails, but they can attempt further attacks against you.",
    "text": "With a wide and sincere smile, you give your attacker pause. You attempt a Diplomacy check against the triggering attacker\u2019s Will DC. After you use Disarming Smile, all creatures who witnessed you use it are temporarily immune to your Disarming Smile for the next 24 hours.",
